Package: ggbiome
Type: Package
Title: Obtain and Plot Whittaker's Biome Information
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Guillem Bagaria, Victor Granda, Georges Kunstler
Maintainer: Guillem Bagaria <g.bagaria@creaf.uab.cat>
Description: R package with functions to obtain mean annual temperature,
    mean annual precipitation and Whittaker's biome type providing geographical
    coordinates, and to plot locations over the biome diagram.
License: GPL (>=2)
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
